      "span_text": "(ii) Phenol extraction. Nucleic acid was extracted from pharyngeal swabs and rubella-infected cell culture supernatants by a standard phenol-chloroform extraction protocol [CITATION_1] . Briefly, 500 l of sample was extracted with 500 l of phenol (Tris equilibrated; pH 8.0) and then with 500 l of chloroform."
